ComicInfo.Title: Artificial Intelligence Part 4
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Artificial Intelligence Part 4: Lightfoot and Lowlight battle Destro and damage his hand; this liberates his artificial hand from Revanche control and he uses it to liberate the Baroness. The Oktober Guard take an airplane out of Trucial Abysnia. Sean celebrates his birthday and Scarlett finds it difficult to see how close he and Dawn are becoming. Zartan gathers the Dreadnoks to inform them of Cobra's plan to brainwash Snake Eyes, which he intends to stop.
